in their bodies.

00:03:02.970 --> 00:03:06.090
Obesity can cause hernias that disrupt

00:03:06.090 --> 00:03:09.940
the anti-reflux barrier of
the gastroesophageal junction

00:03:09.940 --> 00:03:13.530
that normally protects 
against heartburn.

00:03:13.530 --> 00:03:16.340
Numerous medications, 
including those for asthma,

00:03:16.340 --> 00:03:19.770
high blood pressure, birth control, 
and depression

00:03:19.770 --> 00:03:24.350
can also have unintended 
effects on the LES.

00:03:24.350 --> 00:03:27.300
An occasional bout of heartburn isn't

00:03:27.300 --> 00:03:29.370
necessarily something to worry about.

